#

Cold Beet Soup

15 min
$10
150 kcal
Difficulty: 10%
Servings: 4

Allergens:

dairy

Dietary Tags:

vegetariangluten-free

Cuisine:

Eastern European

Course:

Appetizer

Tags:

cold souphealthyvegetable-based

Description

A refreshing cold beet soup, perfect for hot days, loaded with vibrant vegetables and a hint of tanginess.

Ingredients

  • beets, cooked and peeled: 2 cups
  • cucumbers, diced: 1
  • radishes, sliced: 1/2 cup
  • green onions, chopped: 1/4 cup
  • dill, fresh, chopped: 2 tablespoons
  • vegetable broth: 3 cups
  • sour cream: 1/2 cup
  • lemon juice: 2 tablespoons
